1
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:10,400
Why did you save me?

2
00:01:13,599 --> 00:01:14,840
I told you to go.

3
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,480
Why did you turn back?

4
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,400
You can only die in my hands.

5
00:01:24,719 --> 00:01:25,519
Fine.

6
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,040
My life is here.

7
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:32,920
If you want it,

8
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:34,519
just take it.

9
00:01:40,879 --> 00:01:42,599
Now you don't want me to die.

10
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:45,159
Do you have other intentions?

11
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:47,719
Or...

12
00:01:47,959 --> 00:01:48,760
Shen Que.

13
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:51,560
Let me go.

14
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:53,640
I don't want to owe you.

15
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:55,280
Now it's me who saved you.

16
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,159
We owe each other nothing.

17
00:01:58,719 --> 00:02:00,200
When I take your life,

18
00:02:01,079 --> 00:02:02,000
I won't show mercy.

19
00:02:04,959 --> 00:02:06,680
Is it so hard to admit

20
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:09,120
that you care about me?

21
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,039
Shen Que.

22
00:02:36,919 --> 00:02:38,199
The ground is covered in blood.

23
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,639
A'Li, you're hurt.

24
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:43,319
How did you bring him back?

25
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:44,439
It's a long story.

26
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,000
Please help me

27
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,400
save him.

28
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,000
He was badly hurt.

29
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,840
His meridians are damaged.

30
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:02,240
It's hard for mortals to recover.

31
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:04,919
My magic weapon only works on demons,

32
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,319
not on humans.

33
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:08,479
I'm afraid

34
00:03:08,919 --> 00:03:11,159
only the fire phoenix vine can save him.

35
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:17,159
Don't.

36
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:20,039
You need to exchange spiritual power for it.

37
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,680
You have no Spiritual Root.

38
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:23,479
Forcing your Spiritual Power out

39
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,800
will only damage it.

40
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,759
Though it can recover later,

41
00:03:27,439 --> 00:03:28,680
it's still very dangerous.

42
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,159
Fine.

43
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,840
Little Bell Spirit,

44
00:03:33,479 --> 00:03:34,960
help me apply medicine to him first.

45
00:03:36,719 --> 00:03:37,360
Okay.

46
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,960
I'll go get some herbs.

47
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,560
Little White,

48
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:51,560
are you really going to break into the Poshu Hall for him?

49
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:53,199
The Holy Root is still on him.

50
00:03:53,719 --> 00:03:54,759
He can't die now.

51
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,439
Just for the Holy Root?

52
00:04:02,039 --> 00:04:03,039
Are you crazy, Bai?

53
00:04:03,039 --> 00:04:04,439
Since you don't want to get the Holy Root back,

54
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,560
there's no use keeping him alive.

55
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,240
I will get the Holy Root back.

56
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,479
But he saved my life.

57
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,560
I can't just let him die.

58
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:10,800
After this,

59
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,280
I'll have no more debts to him.

60
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,600
I've been with you for a hundred years.

61
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:24,480
yet I never knew you'd remember it so clearly.

62
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,319
If that's the case,

63
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,639
then this time,

64
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:30,920
you owe me.

65
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,360
Bai!

66
00:04:37,199 --> 00:04:38,199
Bai, what are you doing?

67
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,360
Bai!

68
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:40,560
[Bai Weiran,]

69
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:06,399
[Night Butterfly Bai Weiran,]

70
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:10,360
[willing to exchange my spiritual power for the fire phoenix vine.]

71
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:07,000
You...

72
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:09,639
It's just temporary blindness for a few days.

73
00:06:09,959 --> 00:06:10,600
It's nothing.

74
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:13,759
I've repaid

75
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,920
your debt to him.

76
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,319
From now on,

77
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,040
you two are no longer connected.

78
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:22,839
You don't have to go this far for me.

79
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,279
Now, promise me

80
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:27,000
you won't be swayed by Shen Que again.

81
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,480
Please retrieve your Spiritual Root

82
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,480
and restore your power as soon as possible.

83
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:32,759
Take responsibility

84
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,319
and protect the Demon Clan.

85
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,240
Alright,

86
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,360
I promise you.

87
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:45,080
Your wounds are healing well.

88
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,799
Just rest a few more days.

89
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:50,000
Demon hunters are still after you.

90
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,799
You can stay in the demon village.

91
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:54,080
But please don't bother the other pixies.

92
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,080
Is that all?

93
00:08:58,759 --> 00:09:00,559
Don't you have anything else to tell me?

94
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,039
Get some rest.

95
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,960
Miss Meng, my wound...

96
00:09:35,639 --> 00:09:36,519
Why are you here?

97
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,840
What?

98
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:39,039
Disappointed?

99
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:41,720
Eat.

100
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,759
This is the human food

101
00:09:43,759 --> 00:09:44,840
A'Li brought just for you.

102
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:45,960
Where's A'Li?

103
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:48,240
She's taking care of Bai Weiran.

104
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:49,759
Bai Weiran?

105
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,039
He's a demon too?

106
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,159
So what?

107
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,440
To get you the Fire Phoenix Vine,

108
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,240
Little White went to the Poshu Hall alone.

109
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,559
Spiritual damage can make you sick for days.

110
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,559
I made this for you.

111
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:09,879
Take it.

112
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,519
Would you put it on for me?

113
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:29,840
[I heard he risked his life for me,]

114
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:32,480
[but now he'll be blind for days.]

115
00:10:33,639 --> 00:10:34,679
[Now,]

116
00:10:35,919 --> 00:10:38,159
[it's time for me to repay him.]

117
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,159
[Don't worry,]

118
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:43,600
[I'll repay you well.]

119
00:10:43,799 --> 00:10:44,960
My savior!

120
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:51,919
Watch out!

121
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:53,840
Hey.

122
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,360
You don't need to bother with this.

123
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,399
I'll handle it.

124
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:58,480
Come.

125
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:58,960
My savior.

126
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,120
Little White,

127
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:07,480
this is your medicine for today.

128
00:11:07,799 --> 00:11:08,480
Hey.

129
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:10,159
Leave the feeding

130
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:11,320
to me.

131
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:14,519
How can Your Highness, the Prince Xian,

132
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,159
feed medicine to others?

133
00:11:16,159 --> 00:11:17,360
[If possible,]

134
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,080
[I'd rather feed you.]

135
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:23,919
Benefactor,

136
00:11:24,720 --> 00:11:25,799
drink the medicine.

137
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:27,240
Drink it.

138
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:28,480
Drink...

139
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:31,600
Are you alright?

140
00:11:31,879 --> 00:11:32,679
Choked?

141
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:33,639
Are you okay?

142
00:11:47,679 --> 00:11:49,159
What's wrong with you?

143
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,480
Just now,

144
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,879
when he pushed me,

145
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,320
I think

146
00:11:53,559 --> 00:11:55,159
I tore my wound.

147
00:11:55,759 --> 00:11:56,559
It hurts.

148
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,039
A'Li.

149
00:11:59,039 --> 00:11:59,879
I'm here.

150
00:12:01,240 --> 00:12:02,879
Why did you spill the medicine on yourself?

151
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:04,320
I'll take you back to change your clothes.

152
00:12:04,639 --> 00:12:05,159
Okay.

153
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,039
Be careful.

154
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,120
Be careful.

155
00:12:19,039 --> 00:12:19,639
A'Li.

156
00:12:19,919 --> 00:12:21,519
Men and women should keep a distance.

157
00:12:21,759 --> 00:12:23,320
I can handle

158
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,440
giving clothes.

159
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,399
Get out.

160
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:34,039
You can't see.

161
00:12:36,039 --> 00:12:37,279
Can you do it yourself?

162
00:12:40,039 --> 00:12:41,320
Can you see?

163
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:43,440
Aren't you afraid she'll be mad at you?

164
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,639
Not only can I see,

165
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:45,960
I can also take your life.

166
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:47,440
Then it depends on your ability.
